<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.2.9">
<l>muḷḷeyi ṟēyntila kūḻai muṭikoṭā</l>
<l>teḷḷiya ḷeṉpatōr tēcila ḷeṉceykēṉ</l>
<l>kaḷḷaviḻ cōlaik kaṇapuraṅ kaitoḻum</l>
<l>piḷḷaiyaip piḷḷaiyeṉ ṟeṇṇap peṟuvarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Her bud[-like] teeth are not even; [her] hair does not permit a coil.</l>
<l>There is not the glow that is a mature woman. What do I do?</l>
<l>This child who worships, hands [joined],</l>
<l rend="indent">in Kaṇṇapuram with groves where nectar drips,</l>
<l>Do they know to consider that [she] is a child?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
